text:
🌿🏵️A shady quiet pathway lined with tall Trellises displaying a variety of Climbers, some of which are fragranced.
🏵️🍀🪑Rest benches were strategically located where visitors may relax and enjoy the embience.
Great location for jogging. 1 loop is 800m
Cool trellis pathway and provides shade during sunny days.
Nice and many benches for seating.
Bring the mozzie spay. Very tranquil otherwise…
